{"prompt": "Design a corporate site for a cloud storage provider. The design should be secure and use a crisp yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Secure Cloud Storage</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f2f5;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #fec000; /* Crisp Yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #e0a800;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .main-content h2 {\n            color: #e0a800;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            width: 30%;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: left;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #fec000;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #e0a800;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fec000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0a800;\n        }\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(254, 192, 0, 0.7), rgba(224, 168, 0, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/333333/FFFFFF?text=Cloud+Background') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1><i class=\"fas fa-cloud\"></i> SecureCloud</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Data, Secured in the Cloud</h2>\n            <p>Experience unparalleled security, reliability, and accessibility for all your valuable files. With state-of-the-art encryption, your data is protected at every step.</p>\n            <a href=\"#signup\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>Why Choose SecureCloud?</h2>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h3>Military-Grade Encryption</h3>\n                    <p>Your files are protected with advanced AES-256 encryption, both in transit and at rest.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-sync-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Seamless Synchronization</h3>\n                    <p>Access your files from any device, anywhere, with automatic syncing across all your platforms.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Intrusion Detection</h3>\n                    <p>Our robust security infrastructure continuously monitors for and prevents unauthorized access.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-cloud-upload-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Scalable Storage</h3>\n                    <p>From personal documents to enterprise-level data, we offer flexible storage solutions that grow with you.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-headset\"></i>\n                    <h3>24/7 Support</h3>\n                    <p>Our dedicated support team is always available to assist you with any security or storage needs.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield\"></i>\n                    <h3>Access Control</h3>\n                    <p>Granular control over who can access your files, ensuring privacy and compliance.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section id=\"signup\" style=\"background-color: #fec000; padding: 50px 0; text-align: center;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Secure Your Data?</h2>\n            <p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 1.1em;\">Sign up now for a free trial and experience the future of cloud storage.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: #333; border: none;\">Sign Up for Free</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureCloud. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}